Description: This package designed for analyzing deconvolution of the bulk 
      sample(s) using an atlas of reference signature profiles and a selected
      model (non-negative least squares support vector,quadratic programming, or 
      robust linear). Users are given option to create or extend a reference 
      atlas and, also simulate a bulk signature profile of a given size containing
      signatures of cell types. Additionally, methylation data can be used to map
      WGBS methylation data to probe IDs using BSmeth2Probe function. Users can 
      also convert any methylKit objects (except for methylDiff) to GRanges with
      convertMe function.
